  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-05 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. Embeds weakener W-AR-05 (comparator absence/mismatch): one validation result omits the comparedAgainst link entirely, and the comparator used in the second result was derived from steady-state in-vitro experiments, whereas the declared COU requires pulsatile flow representative of CPB operation. The inference method mismatch (D3 undercutting) is stated explicitly in the validation narrative.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cpb-hemolysis-rh-criterion",
